Privacy Policy for Daily App

Last Updated: February 1st, 2024

Thank you for choosing Daily App! This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, disclose, and manage your personal information when you use our mobile application.

	•	Information We Collect:
	•	Account Information:
When you sign up for Daily App, we collect your name, email address, and password to create and manage your account.
	•	Location Information:
To provide you with personalized restaurant options, we may collect your device's location with your consent.
	•	Order Information:
We collect information about your orders, including the items selected, payment details, and delivery preferences.

	•	How We Use Your Information:
	•	Provide Services
We use your information to offer and improve our services, including displaying nearby restaurants and processing your orders.
	•	Personalization:
Your location information helps us tailor restaurant recommendations to your area.
	•	Communication:
We may send you notifications, updates, and promotional messages related to our services.
	•	Information Sharing:
	•	With Restaurants:
Your order details, including delivery address, are shared with the selected restaurant to fulfill your order.
	•	Service Providers:
We may share information with third-party service providers for purposes such as payment processing and order delivery.
	•	Legal Compliance:
We may disclose your information if required by law or in response to legal requests.





	•	Security:
	•	Data Security:
We implement security measures to protect your information from unauthorized access and maintain the confidentiality of your account.
	•	Payment Security:
For online payments, we use secure and trusted third-party payment processors to ensure the security of your financial information.
	•	Your Choices:
	•	Location Settings:
You can control your location settings through your device settings or within the app.
6. Updates to Privacy Policy:
We may update this Privacy Policy to reflect changes in our practices. Please review the policy periodically for any updates.
By using Daily App, you agree to the terms outlined in this Privacy Policy.
